      "content": "i know i should talk to someone but it just feels like another thing to do. just another chore on an endless list. it's like... what's even the point of trying to fix something that's just fundamentally broken? if the world wasn't built for me, then maybe i'm just not supposed to be in it. it's just so much easier to imagine just... not having to fight anymore. to just be still.",
